{"prompt": "Generate a website for a professional law firm. The website should be rustic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Sterling & Stone Law</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #3b5998; /* A deep, rustic blue */\n            --secondary-color: #8b9dc3; /* A muted, complementary blue */\n            --text-color: #f0f0f0; /* Light text for contrast */\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --footer-color: #2d3436; /* Dark footer */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: #333;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            margin-top: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/3b5998/ffffff?text=Professional+Legal+Services'); /* Placeholder for a rustic background image */\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 0;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-color: rgba(59, 89, 152, 0.6); /* Darker overlay for better text readability */\n        }\n\n        .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n\n        .service-item p {\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 5px 0;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info p {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Sterling & Stone Law</h1>\n            <p>Your trusted advisors in legal matters</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n            <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Experience, Integrity, Justice</h2>\n            <p>Providing expert legal counsel with a commitment to your success.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>About Sterling & Stone</h2>\n        <p style=\"line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.1em;\">\n            Founded on principles of diligence and unwavering dedication, Sterling & Stone Law has been serving our clients with exceptional legal expertise for over two decades. We understand that navigating legal challenges can be daunting, which is why we offer personalized attention and clear, straightforward advice. Our team of seasoned attorneys is committed to achieving the best possible outcomes for every client, fostering trust and building lasting relationships.\n        </p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Services</h2>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>Corporate Law</h3>\n            <p>From formation and compliance to mergers and acquisitions, we provide comprehensive legal support for your business.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>Real Estate Law</h3>\n            <p>Expert guidance on property transactions, zoning, development, and landlord-tenant disputes.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>Litigation</h3>\n            <p>Aggressive and effective representation in civil and commercial disputes, ensuring your rights are protected.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>Estate Planning</h3>\n            <p>Secure your legacy with our tailored wills, trusts, and probate services.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <div class=\"contact-info\">\n            <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Law Lane, Metropolis, CA 90210</p>\n            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890</p>\n            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:info@sterlingstonelaw.com\">info@sterlingstonelaw.com</a></p>\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 0.9em; margin-top: 20px;\">We offer free initial consultations.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Sterling & Stone Law. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Disclaimer: Legal information on this site is not legal advice. Consult with an attorney for advice specific to your situation.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple scroll-to-section functionality\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}